<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #333;
      margin: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #b30000; /* Dark Red */
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    ul {
      margin-left: 20px;
      list-style-type: square;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Styling for sections */
    h1 {
      border-bottom: 2px solid #b30000;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      background-color: #b30000;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Link Styling */
    a {
      color: #b30000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Box for highlighting key information */
    .highlight {
      background-color: #ffcccc; /* Light Red */
      padding: 10px;
      border-left: 4px solid #b30000;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>Welcome to our privacy policy. Your privacy is critically important to us.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect personal information from users who list or book properties on our platform. This includes, but is not limited to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Phone number</li>
    <li>Payment details</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Facilitate property bookings and listings</li>
    <li>Process payments securely</li>
    <li>Improve our services</li>
    <li>Communicate with users about their bookings</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
  <p>We do not share personal information with third parties, except:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>When it is necessary to complete a booking</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    <li>With trusted third-party service providers who assist us in delivering services</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the information we hold about you</li>
    <li>Request corrections to your information</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your personal data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <div class="highlight">
    <b>We Adopt No Canellation Policy Due To High Demand In Bookings And As Convenience Fee With Regards In Booking.</b>
    <p><b>We may update our privacy policy from time to time. We encourage users to review this page regularly to stay informed about how we protect their information.</b><br>
    </p>
  </div>
